pour w PGE Skrze Be\u0142chat\u00f3w''] \u2013 onet.pl \u2013 10-08-2017</ref> Milad achieved bronze medal of the [[2017 FIVB Volleyball Men's World Grand Champions Cup|2017 World Grand Champions Cup]] and he received individual award for the Best Outside Spiker of the tournament.<ref>[https://www.fivb.org/viewPressRelease.asp?No=72981&Language=en#.WcfV_Vu0PIU ''World Grand Champions Cup: Iran take bronze with 3-2 win over France''] \u2013 fivb.org \u2013 17-09-2017</ref>\n\n==Sporting achievements==\n* '''[[AVC Club Volleyball Championship|AVC Asian Club Championship]]'''\n** [[File:Gold medal asia.svg|16px]] [[2013 Asian Men's Club Volleyball Championship|Iran 2013]] \u2013 with [[Kalleh Mazandaran VC|Kalleh Mazandaran]]\n** [[File:Gold medal asia.svg|16px]] [[2016 Asian Men's Club Volleyball Championship|Myanmar 2016]] \u2013 with [[Sarmayeh Bank Tehran VC|Sarmayeh Bank Tehran]]\n** [[File:Gold medal asia.svg|16px]] [[2017 Asian Men's Club Volleyball Championship|Vietnam 2017]] \u2013 with [[Sarmayeh Bank Tehran VC|Sarmayeh Bank Tehran]]\n\n* '''National championships'''\n** '''2012/2013''' [[File:Gold medal with cup.svg|16px]] [[2012-13 Iranian Volleyball Super League|Iranian Championship]], with [[Kalleh Mazandaran VC|Kalleh Mazandaran]]\n** '''2013/2014''' [[File:Silver medal with cup.svg|16px]] [[2013-14 Iranian Volleyball Super League|Iranian Championship]], with [[Kalleh Mazandaran VC|Kalleh Mazandaran]]\n** '''2014/2015''' [[File:Silver medal with cup.svg|16px]] [[2014-15 Iranian Volleyball Super League|Iranian Championship]], with [[Shahrdari Urmia VC|Shahrdari Urmia]]\n** '''2015/2016''' [[File:Bronze medal with cup.svg|16px]] [[2015-16 Iranian Volleyball Super League|Iranian Championship]], with [[Shahrdari Urmia VC|Shahrdari Urmia]]\n** '''2016/2017''' [[File:Gold medal with cup.svg|16px]] [[2016-17 Iranian Volleyball Super League|Iranian Championship]], with [[Sarmayeh Bank Tehran VC|Sarmayeh Bank Tehran]]\n** '''2016/2017''' [[File:Simple gold cup.sv